cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.GR, cs.CG, cs.MM

Reasoning: 
1. cs.CV (Computer Vision) is the most likely category as the paper deals with real-time 3D scanning and pose estimation using RGB-D input. 
2. cs.RO (Robotics) is also likely as the paper mentions the importance of 3D scanning for robotic applications. 
3. cs.GR (Graphics) is another possible category as the paper deals with 3D reconstruction and surface re-integration. 
4. cs.CG (Computational Geometry) is a possible category as the paper deals with geometric and photometric matching for pose estimation. 
5. cs.MM (Multimedia) is a possible category as the paper deals with real-time processing of RGB-D input for 3D scanning.
